Package de.esoco.lib.json

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonSerializable<J extends JsonSerializable<J>>
    An interface for objects that can be serialized to and from the JSON data format.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Json
    Contains declarations and functions for the handling of JSON data.
    JsonArray
    An extension of ArrayList that also implements JsonSerializable so that it can be used directly in JSON expressions.
    JsonBuilder
    A builder for JSON strings that can append arbitrary data objects to a JSON string.
    JsonBuilder.ConvertJson
    An invertible function to convert objects to (JsonBuilder.ConvertJson.evaluate(Object)) and from (JsonBuilder.ConvertJson.invert(String) JSON.
    JsonObject
    A generic JSON object that provides access methods for JSON datatypes.
    JsonParser
    A parser for the JSON data that can also be used to parse the relations of Relatable objects.
    JsonRelatedObject<J extends JsonRelatedObject<J>>
    A Relatable implementation that has direct support for serialization to and from JSON.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Json.JsonStructure
    Enumeration of the available JSON structures.
